      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00002",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "昨日里在江楼把酒饮，只吃得醉醺醺转回牢城。迈步儿且把小营房进，等待了戴贤弟把话来云。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00003",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "戴宗上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00004",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "载宗"
      ],
      "text": "忙将衙中事，报与大哥知。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00005",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "呀，贤弟来了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00006",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "大哥，大事不好了！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00007",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "何事惊慌？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00008",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "只因昨日，大哥在浔阳楼上饮酒，酒后在粉壁墙上，曾题反诗一首，被那黄文炳看见，报与州官知道。适才将小弟唤进衙去，叫小弟将大哥拿到州衙，问出口供，就要就地正法！",
      "text_length": 78
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00009",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00010",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "就地正法！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00011",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江昏厥。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00012",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "大哥醒来！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00013",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "听一言不由人三魂渺渺，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00014",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00015",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "吓得我魂灵儿飞上九霄。走向前来忙跪倒，望贤弟搭救我性命一条。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00016",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，你要快快想一妙计，搭救愚兄性命才好！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00017",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "事到如今，哪有妙计？大哥你快快打扮作一疯汉，混他一时，再作道理。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00018",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "事到如今，只好如此。正是：",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00019",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "闭门家中坐，祸从天上来。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00020",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "大哥速速改扮，小弟要少陪了。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00021",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "请便。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00022",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "戴宗下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00023",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "待我改扮起来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00024",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00025",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二差役同上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00026",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "奉了太爷命，捉拿造反人。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00027",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "伙计，咱们太爷叫拿造反之人，叫什么葱姜？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00028",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役乙"
      ],
      "text": "宋江。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00029",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "不错，宋江。这宋江，他到底在什么地方呀？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00030",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "戴宗上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00031",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "你们敢是去拿宋江的么？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00032",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00033",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "来来来，随我来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00034",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "好，正在为难的时候，偏偏遇见戴院长啦，不然我们一辈子也找不着他！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00035",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "戴宗"
      ],
      "text": "到了。宋江想必正在里面。我少陪了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00036",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "请便请便。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00037",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "待我喊叫一声。我说宋江，你出来！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00038",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "乔装改扮安排定，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00039",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00040",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "假装疯魔有病人。悔不该在江楼来把酒饮，无故地题诗句惹下祸根。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00041",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役乙"
      ],
      "text": "宋江，你出来！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00042",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "我这里迈步来忙观定，却原来是我的结发人。叫一声贤妻你来得好，你我到房中叙一叙恩情。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00043",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "你是他的媳妇呀？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00044",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役乙"
      ],
      "text": "你才是他的媳妇哪！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00045",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "我是他媳妇的爹！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00046",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "扭回头来把话论，却原来是岳父到我门。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00047",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役乙"
      ],
      "text": "你原来是他的丈人呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00048",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "得啦！别玩笑。我说宋江，太爷传你哪，跟着我们走吧。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00049",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "叫岳父与贤妻把路引，你我一同见圣君。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00050",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江、二差役同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00051",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四青袍、州官同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00052",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "奉了太尊令，审问造反人。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00053",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "差役甲上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00054",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "text": "启太爷：宋江拿到。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00055",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "青袍官甲"
      ],
      "text": "带上来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00056",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "差役乙押宋江同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00057",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "我大摇大摆往前进，上面厢坐的是对头人。我撩袍端带上龙庭，问我一言我答一声。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00058",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "胆大宋江，见了本州为何不跪？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00059",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "你是何等样人，我岂能跪你！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00060",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "你在酒楼题了反诗，你要从实招来！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00061",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "想我宋江，乃是天神下界。吾奉玉帝敕旨，带领十万天兵天将，去至京城，扫荡奸臣。我不久就是皇帝了。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00062",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "我奉上方玉帝令，带领十万鬼神兵。除却朝中众奸佞，一统山河我坐朝廷。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00063",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "看宋江，满口疯话，但不知是真是假。呵哈有了：待我将些尿粪臭秽之物，叫他去用，若是吃，便是真疯；他若不吃，便是装就。来！",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00064",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "有！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00065",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "将尿粪抬一桶上来。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00066",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00067",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二差役同下，抬桶同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00068",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "嘿，好臭好臭！粪抬到。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00069",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "青袍官甲"
      ],
      "text": "宋江，你莫要欺哄本州。堂下有粪水一桶，你去用来。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00070",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "呵哈，哈哈哈！我今到此，你还要费心设宴。好，待我用来。喝喝，我就叨扰了。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00071",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "多谢兄台太多情，来此还要设席珍。众位何妨同来请，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00072",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二差役"
      ],
      "text": "这样的好东西，你请吧，我们没有这个造化。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00073",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "他一个一个就不应声。看起来你等无福分，他不识海味与山珍。我这里抓一把就四面洒，",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00074",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "有道是“主不请，客不饮”，你请用啊！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00075",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "宋江"
      ],
      "text": "我洒他个满堂乱纷纷！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00076",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "宋江向四周泼洒粪水。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00077",
      "play_id": "01014003",
      "scene_id": "01014003_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "州官"
      ],
      "text": "来！将宋江暂且收禁，待我禀报蔡大老爷，任他发落便了。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014003_e00078",
